      • isServiceCheckSupported

        public boolean isServiceCheckSupported()
        Gets whether the service represented by this response supports running "Service Checks". A service check is possible where there is a custom command defined in the metainfo.xml of the service definition. This not the same as a custom command defined for a component.
        Returns:
        true if this service supports running "Service Checks", false otherwise.
